        "can_wiki": false,
        "cooked": "<p>Hi, Is it not possible to use the import() openscad function to import an stl for a parametric model? i uploaded my stl file to the model (oven_knob_solid.stl), then uploaded the scad file (oven_knob.scad) but it just fails validation. I am referencing the stl in the scad file using</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>import(\u201coven_knob_solid.stl\u201d);</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Thanks</p>",
        "created_at": "2026-04-08T19:26:20.483Z",
