        "cooked": "<p>If it fails validation, run the stl through a repair tool to ensure it is manifold.  openscad can\u2019t handle broken solids.</p>\n<p>Otherwise, should be ok.  Additive operations work well but it can struggle on subtractive depending on your solid.  If youre using windows beware strings and filepaths.  escape your backslashes, keep it on the same drive, mind your case sensitivity.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/original/3X/8/f/8f6f8330eca34a4da4f48e12a3b8e73a7eb1f4b0.png\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/ksTbWsVUhD0RIXXfpNWWwv25UnC.png?dl=1\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/8/f/8f6f8330eca34a4da4f48e12a3b8e73a7eb1f4b0_2_690x396.png\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"ksTbWsVUhD0RIXXfpNWWwv25UnC\" width=\"690\" height=\"396\" srcset=\"https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/8/f/8f6f8330eca34a4da4f48e12a3b8e73a7eb1f4b0_2_690x396.png, https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/original/3X/8/f/8f6f8330eca34a4da4f48e12a3b8e73a7eb1f4b0.png 1.5x, https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/original/3X/8/f/8f6f8330eca34a4da4f48e12a3b8e73a7eb1f4b0.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"E7E0B4\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">972\u00d7559 101 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
